{
  "stem": "6777.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, something came from selling off things which we still had, like valuable pictures or jewelry or-- and then I worked a bit, too.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My word. ?]",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For some time, I worked in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] was Warsaw city cleaning department.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They've been sending out cleaning trucks with water in the streets and this sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because my friends from the resistance-- they were there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I got in there, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I got in only part time, not permanently.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was enough to put on a front-- to put up a front that you have--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She got one.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A false one.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it wasn't terribly good, but-- I remember going every two, three days into the market, and horse flesh-- horse meat, which is lovely, you know?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Horse meat, when you make it properly, it's beautiful.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I really got to like it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And vegetable.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, because the radios-- they all had-- the resistance people, they had the radios.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not only did we know, but we traced on the map how the Russian front is coming closer, where they are now and--",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Do you--?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have been in contact with my friends from the council, the Lichtenbaums.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They'd been transported to the Lublin Ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they've been not straightaway put into the gas chambers, into Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they've been kept in the arbeitslager, in the work camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I kept in contact with them through a driver from the Judenrat, from the council's car, a driver.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When the council-- when the ghettos stopped existing, he was still a friend.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And through him, I kept in contact.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He drove to Lublin and got through his friends some message to the people.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
